Efficiently Summarize a Customer Interaction (Beta)

Use Einstein Copilot to eliminate the manual effort required to summarize a customer interaction and free the time of contact center agents to assist more customers.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in clouds where Einstein Copilot is available.

Who: To use this feature, users need the Industry Service Excellence, Digital Engagement, and Service Cloud Voice add-on licenses.

How: To summarize a customer interaction, submit an utterance in Einstein Copilot from an Engagement Interaction, a Messaging Session, or a Voice Call record page.
